{"tid":1281042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一位83歲嘅婆婆比大家嘅說話","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:24:13.000Z","uid":213208,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0c2aae6e131518f2f363c9fec2e9046aee71c5","tid":1281042,"uid":213208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"大概內容都係話<br />\n呢代年輕人真係好好 我好支持你地<br />\n多謝你地肯為香港發聲 <br />\n<br />\n佢一路豎起手指公 一路讚我地<br />\n呢個幾月黎都係咁講 仲叫我地小心唔好再有事<br />\n香港搞成日 佢話佢都好心痛<br />\n<br />\n聽佢講完 真係眼濕濕<br />\n可能佢唔係完全明發生緊嘅事<br />\n但佢知道我地係為我地嘅香港而抗爭<br />\n連80幾歲嘅老人家都明白 點解而家啲真廢老仲係唔明<br />\n<br />\n嫲嫲多謝你 我愛你"},{"pid":"2ab40e2b7988c593ffd496af000ebd33d485f5b0","tid":1281042,"uid":216433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"老而不廢"},{"pid":"f78f9bbdcbc8837b4841897fac427de7155400a7","tid":1281042,"uid":135798,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"呢位先係令人值得尊重嘅老人家<br />\n希望你嫲嫲身體健康 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n630出去嗰班？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901120c1c1d761852c2e892cf582c44e48b19faa","tid":1281042,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能佢同佢上一代都俾土共迫害過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01351a9af158d08060735df647a4bf7395a556a","tid":1281042,"uid":213208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"901120c1c1d761852c2e892cf582c44e48b19faa","tid":1281042,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能佢同佢上一代都俾土共迫害過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"係，佢話佢個代都冇人敢出聲<br />\n知道係幾黑暗"},{"pid":"47653e1fce16895e506909853567603f0e304046","tid":1281042,"uid":245409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"其實係而家為人父母，仔大女大果班先多數係藍絲廢老<br />\n<br />\n呀爺呀嫲級果d係好僧警察，同埋好多係走難落黎，咩原因走落黎大家都知<br />\n<br />\n反而父母叔伯果堆，雖然係捱左大半生，但相對佢地當時身處黃金年代既香港，個個掛住搵錢，亦無而家既強權統治，對政治冷感或偏幫政府同黑警都係正常，平心而論，警隊本身聲譽係越黎越良好，但係14年果下己經近乎一舖清袋"},{"pid":"2610af5f8a2ec31240fadaed6c4f126d201ce377","tid":1281042,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"每次見到有明白事理嘅老人家都好感動，佢地係難得嘅清泉"},{"pid":"b1141566604389a3dec2c564d66f9a2f014df1e8","tid":1281042,"uid":161560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"上次律政有個婆婆叫我地加油<br />\n佢靠晒我哋呢班後生<br />\n<br />\n之後行開咗，本身以為佢要走<br />\n點知過咗陣佢拎住咗兩大袋m記返嚟"},{"pid":"2e5d91148ffa304aea41f4a33fb80ab473c75c53","tid":1281042,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b01351a9af158d08060735df647a4bf7395a556a","tid":1281042,"uid":213208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"901120c1c1d761852c2e892cf582c44e48b19faa","tid":1281042,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能佢同佢上一代都俾土共迫害過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"係，佢話佢個代都冇人敢出聲<br />\n知道係幾黑暗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"的確果陣冇乜時機發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo